# Validate patch before applying

When using `propose_patch`, always follow it with `validate_patch` before writing any changes to disk.

`validate_patch` confirms the patch plan is structurally sound, targets the correct symbols, and will not produce broken imports or missing references. Skipping this step risks introducing silent breakage.
